        "content": "<p>hashimoto-kei edited <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/11329\">PR #11329</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>I don't think an issue is needed for this. Just a brief notice that a new terminal needs to be opened after <code>wastime</code> installation.</p>\n<p>Why</p>\n<p><code>wasmtime</code> cannot be executed unless user profile is reloaded.</p>\n<p><div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Bash\"><pre><span></span><code>$<span class=\"w\"> </span>curl<span class=\"w\"> </span>https://wasmtime.dev/install.sh<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sSf<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>bash\n$<span class=\"w\"> </span>wasmtime<span class=\"w\"> </span>-V\nzsh:<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">command</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>not<span class=\"w\"> </span>found:<span class=\"w\"> </span>wasmtime\n</code></pre></div><br>\n</p>\n</blockquote>",
